Name: HubSpot CRM Contacts
Description: Work with contacts/leads in the HubSpot CRM
Share Context: HubSpot CRM Context from ./tool.gpt
Tools: Create Contact, Get Contact, Delete Contact, Update Contact, Search Contacts
Tools: ./associations.gpt, ./properties.gpt, ./owners.gpt
Params: prompt: detailed request to be executed against the HubSpot API

Fulfill the users request: ${PROMPT}

Use the tools available to you.

---
Name: Create Contact
Description: Creates a new contact/lead in the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: properties: a json object with all the properties of the contact

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/createContact.py

---
Name: Get Contact
Description: Retrieves a contact by ID from the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: contact_id: the ID of the contact to retrieve

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/getContact.py

---
Name: Delete Contact
Description: Deletes a contact by ID from the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: contact_id: the ID of the contact to delete

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/deleteContact.py

---
Name: Update Contact
Description: Updates an existing contact/lead in the HubSpot CRM by ID
Credential: ./credential
Tools: HubSpot CRM Get Properties from properties.gpt
Params: contact_id: the ID of the contact to update
Params: properties: a json object with all the properties to update. Each key in the json must be a valid property name returned by the 'HubSpot CRM Get Properties' tool.

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/updateContact.py

---
Name: Search Contacts
Description: Searches for contacts/leads in the HubSpot CRM
Credential: ./credential
Params: filters: a json object with one or more keys in the format `{"<PROPERTY_NAME>":"<VALUE_TO_SEARCH_FOR>"}`. Each key in the json must be a valid property name returned by the 'HubSpot CRM Get Properties' tool.

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/searchContacts.py
